      "x": 416, "y": 922,
      "width": 308, "height": 100,
      "text": "run_test.sh  (dispatcher)\n\n1  source defaults.env  (caller env wins)\n2  uv venv + requirements.txt  (per-suite)\n3  _helpers/wait_for_server.sh $TARGET\n4  fetch_server_info.sh → $SERVER_INFO\n5  exec <suite>/run.sh",
      "originalText": "run_test.sh  (dispatcher)\n\n1  source defaults.env  (caller env wins)\n2  uv venv + requirements.txt  (per-suite)\n3  _helpers/wait_for_server.sh $TARGET\n4  fetch_server_info.sh → $SERVER_INFO\n5  exec <suite>/run.sh",
